.NET Framework 3.5.name: VRTK_ClimbableGrabAttach
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: The Climbable Grab Attach script is used to mark the object as a climbable interactable object.
.NET Framework 3.5.example: VRTK/Examples/037_CameraRig_ClimbingFalling uses this grab attach mechanic for each item that is climbable in the scene.
